flowchart LR
    Client[Web Client / React]
    Router[API Router / Controllers]
    AuthMW[Auth Middleware\nBearer-token validation]
    RBAC[Authorization / RBAC Policy]

    DocSvc[Document Service]
    VersionSvc[Version / Revert Logic]
    PermissionSvc[Permission Service]
    AISvc[AI Job Service]
    ExportSvc[Export Job Service]
    SessionSvc[Session Service]

    UsersRepo[Users Repository]
    DocsRepo[Documents Repository]
    PermRepo[Permissions Repository]
    AIRepo[AI / Policy Repository]
    ExportRepo[Exports Repository]
    Audit[Audit Logger]

    DB[(SQLite Database)]
    RT[Realtime Sync Service\nWebSocket / CRDT Gateway]
    LLM[AI Provider / LLM API]
    IdP[Identity Provider\nTarget architecture]

    Client -->|REST routes| Router
    Router --> AuthMW --> RBAC

    Router --> DocSvc
    Router --> VersionSvc
    Router --> PermissionSvc
    Router --> AISvc
    Router --> ExportSvc
    Router --> SessionSvc

    DocSvc --> DocsRepo
    DocSvc --> Audit
    VersionSvc --> DocsRepo
    VersionSvc --> Audit
    VersionSvc --> RT
    PermissionSvc --> PermRepo
    PermissionSvc --> Audit
    PermissionSvc --> RT
    AISvc --> AIRepo
    AISvc --> Audit
    AISvc --> LLM
    ExportSvc --> ExportRepo
    ExportSvc --> Audit
    SessionSvc --> DocsRepo
    SessionSvc --> PermRepo
    SessionSvc --> UsersRepo

    UsersRepo --> DB
    DocsRepo --> DB
    PermRepo --> DB
    AIRepo --> DB
    ExportRepo --> DB
    Audit --> DB
    AuthMW -.-> IdP
